ime":"2017-01-19T04:19:53.000Z","msg":"未離開過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50a5fa6b73282011a36d926dbb1b87d11e282eb","tid":86313,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未離開過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c684e0f4b97a8ac11381deaddd194c64273b36","tid":86313,"uid":6071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"我係箍牙嘅套餐包埋嘅 手細幾好 局部麻醉 係智慧牙未出黎個陣就剝左 剝嘅時候唔痛 不過之後痛足一個禮拜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  剝完之後食唔到飯 勁驚d 飯跌左落個傷口度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bae9063d1b9d17f142e163f3a00e7132a75c01","tid":86313,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開始 要去菲臘門診先定私家可以轉介</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n有冇巴打知應該點做？"},{"pid":"707a0c35a50e37714bc64a45f263f87dade5abb2","tid":86313,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一開始 要去菲臘門診先定私家可以轉介</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n有冇巴打知應該點做？</blockquote><br />\n應該唔洗轉介吧，我都冇人轉介，諗住凌晨去排隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fb97ca5fda6e66edb3575a8b3112cf2262ea2b","tid":86313,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n菲臘牙科醫院做</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪局部麻醉就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無全身比你做<br />\n打2支針入牙 試下痛唔痛就去馬<br />\n支針最撚痛 <br />\n之後完左番到屋企又係好撚痛 痛足一日</blockquote><br />\n好驚我唔痛嘅話會排好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東區牙科嗰邊排期，醫生話要兩年先有得剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n箍完牙唔想等到d牙歪曬先搞"},{"pid":"a9ab06ae594869f497fb32e23c8b8fff637df53a","tid":86313,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一開始 要去菲臘門診先定私家可以轉介</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n有冇巴打知應該點做？</blockquote><br />\n應該唔洗轉介吧，我都冇人轉介，諗住凌晨去排隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上網睇左8:15開始派籌 巴打噤有恆心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗住朝早去碰下運氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc92cc2673fa2383594ebfe37820e411cd4b182c","tid":86313,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3101edb82791e8581e1ddeade83c1849e496860","tid":86313,"uid":568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n菲臘牙科醫院做</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪局部麻醉就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無全身比你做<br />\n打2支針入牙 試下痛唔痛就去馬<br />\n支針最撚痛 <br />\n之後完左番到屋企又係好撚痛 痛足一日</blockquote><br />\n千其唔好望支針有幾粗<br />\n望完仲痛"},{"pid":"d0749b4c70801698dae1e2a9d40a056f202deee4","tid":86313,"uid":568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"Btw 全身好傷身 <br />\n好易爆腎/肝"},{"pid":"b5574e27a58eed7e25c96baddefac79b00800de9","tid":86313,"uid":86791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有2隻打橫生，未痛，但因為啱啱箍完牙，有一隻大牙已經頂歪左，想早d剝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 